  I . In3 li2 sou2 kong2 e5 chho3-gou7 . 
  1 . Li2 kong2 Sun3 kiaN-liau2 oe7 bo5 lang5 thang che3-su7 chiah chiong5-koan5 chhoa7 Giau5 e5 kong-chu2 . To m7-chai kong2 si7 in-ui7 kiaN- liau2 bo5 lang5 thang soa3-chiap i-e5 chiok- thou2 , Sun3-tian2 pou2-bong5 hit-pho7-chheh kiam2 sian-siN iau2-be7 thak8-ke3 , mih-sai2 ke kong2 choe7-choe7 oe7 . 
  2 . Li2 kong2 Thong in-ui7 Kat-pek bo5 che3 , chiah khi3 hoat8--i , Bu2-ong5 in-ui7 Tiu7 bo5 che3 , chiu7 khi3 phah--i . Iah8-si7 su7-si7 ji5- hui . Beng7-chu2 kong2 , “ U7 gin2-a2 koaN7 soe2-a2 kap bah beh khi3 chhan5--nih8 hou7 lang5 chiah8 , Kat-pek thai5--i , chiong mih8 chhiuN2-khi3 , ” e7-bin7 chiu7 kong2 , “ Thong in-ui7 i thai5 chit-e5 gin2-a2 , chiah khi3 cheng--i . ” An2-ni chiu7 khi2-peng e5 ian5- kou3 si7 in-ui7 Kat-pek thai5 bo5 choe7 e5 gin2- a2 , m7-si7 in-ui7 i bo5 che3 . Koh Bu2-ong5 oe7 khi3 hoat8 Tiu7 , iah8 m7-si7 in-ui7 i bo5 che3 ; sui-bong2 Su-keng Thai3-se7 hit phiN u7 kong2 , “ Tiu7 pang3-sak i-e5 sian-chou2 , chong- biau7 bo5 che3-su7 , kap kong2 che3 bo5 li7-ek , kau-sia7 bo5 siu-cheng2 , chong-biau7 bo5 che3 ” , --- chiah e5 oe7 , chong2-si7 Bu2-ong5 teh hiam5 Tiu7 e5 m7-tioh8 , m7 na7 chit8-hang7 ; kong2-khi2 bo5 che3 e5 tai7-chi3 , put-ko3 nng7 saN ku3 chhap ti7 hi2 lai7-bin7, kho2-kian3 m7- si7 liah8 chit-hang7 choe3 iau3-kin2 chiah khi3 hoat8--i . Koh Kat-pek thai5-su Thong , Tiu7 thai5-su Bu2-ong5 iah8 m7-si7 tui3 bo5 che3 ; siat-su2 in nng7-lang5 oe7 siu-sin, che5-ka , eng7 gau5-lang5 , thiaN3 peh-siN3 , chiu7 Thong Bu2 tek-khak bo5 in-ui7 i bo5 che3 khi3 phah i , siat-su2 khi3 phah i iah8 boe7 oe7 iaN5. Beng7-chu2 kong2, “ Kiat8 Tiu7 sit-loh8 thiN-e7 , si7 in-ui7 sit-loh8 peh-siN3 . ” Koh kong2, “ Sam- tai7 tit-tioh8 thiN-e7 si7 in-ui7 jin5-tek , sit- loh8 thiN-e7 si7 in-ui7 bo5 jin5-tek; ” long2 bo5 kong2 si7 in-ui7 bo5 che3 . ChhiaN2 khoaN3 kin-a2-jit8 e5 Thian-tiok , An-lam5, Siam7-lo5 , Bian2-tian7 long2 u7 che3 chou2-kong e5 tai7- chi3 , na7 che3 chou2-kong chin-chiaN3 si7 hap8 Thian-i3 , chiu7 tioh8 thai3-peng5 an-lok8 , kok pu3 , bin5 kiong5 . Su-keng kong2, “ Sun7 to7-li2 chiu7 ho2 ” . ChaiN2-iuN7-a2 hoan2-tng2 hou7 kui2- pah ni5 lai5 Au-chiu bo5 che3 e5 Eng-kok Hoat-kok koan2 ah ? 
  3 . Li2 kong2 Siong7-te3 e5 pun2-goan5 si7 na2 chui2 e5 Seng-siu3 hai2 , soaN e5 Khun-lun5, pun2-goan5 sui-bong2 si7 , m7-ku2 chin7-chai7 hng7 , sou2-i2 bo5 hok8-sai7 si7 bo5 iau3-kin2 . Hai7 ah ! Li2 chin7 poe7-pun2, i2-keng chai i si7 pun2-goan5 chiah m7 hok8-sai7 , che si7 sim2- mih8 to7-li2 ? Siat-su2 li2 u7 kiaN2 chhut-goa7 khi3 Kim-soaN li7-khui li2 kui2-na7 ban7 li2 , li2 kiam2 bo5 si5-si5 ng3-bang7 i kia3 gun5 to3-lai5 choe3 ke-lai7 e5 sou2-hui3 ? Siat-su2 i phah-sng3 kong2 , Pe7-bu2 khiok si7 siN--goa2, io--goa2 , chhi7--goa2 , hou7 goa2 toa7 , chong2-si7 saN li7- khui to kang2-ban7 li2 oh-tit tioh8 , tui3 an2- ni kio3 pat8-lang5 choe3 pe7 , kio3 pat8-lang5 choe3 bu2 , kio3 pat8-lang5 choe3 hiaN-ti7, sian- siN li2 u7 hoaN-hi2 mah ? Lun7 hok8-sai7 Siong7- te3 kiam2 si7 gun2 e5 kau3 sou2 siat--e5 ? Beng7-chu2 kong2 , “ Sui-bong2 u7 phaiN2-lang5 chai- kai3 bok8-iok8 iah8 thang hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 . ” Liat8-chu2 e5 chheh kong2 , “ U7 chit8-e5 Song3- kok e5 lang5 ai3 kiaN5 jin5-gi7 e5 tai7-chi3 , saN- tai7 lang5 bo5 ia3-sian7, ke-lai7 bo5 ian5-kou3 , ou-gu5 siN peh8-gu5 , lai5 mng7 Khong2-chu2 , Khong2- chu2 kong2 , Che si7 ho2 tiau7-thau5 thang hian3 hou7 Siong7-te3. ” An2-ni chiu7 chai cha2 iah8 u7 lang5 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 , m7-si7 jin5-kun u7 na7-tiaN7 , peh-siN3 iah8 u7 ; si7 kau3 Beng5-tiau5 Hong5-bu2 chiah kim3 peh-siN3 m7-thang ki5- to2 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 , chi2-u7 jin5-kun thang na7-tiaN7 , chong2-si7 che si7 i-e5 toa7 chho3 . Siong7-te3 si7 na2 lau7-pe7, toe7-bin7-chiuN7 cheng3-lang5 si7 na2-chun2 kiaN2 , jin5-kun si7 na2-chun2 toa7-kiaN2, kiam2 toa7-kiaN2 thang oa2-kun7 i-e5 pe7 , ki5-u5 e5 kiaN2 thang sng3 i-e5 pe7 choe3 pat8-lang5 ? Sou2-i2 lun7-kau3 Siong7-te3 si7 cheng3-lang5 sou2 eng-kai hok8-sai7--e5 ; siat-su2 Siong7-te3 chin-chiaN3 li7 lan2 hng7 , iu5-goan5 tioh8 hok8-sai7 i , ho5-hong3 kap lan2 kun7-kun7 , in-ui7 lan2 kho3 i lai5 oah8 , lai5 ti7- teh , lai5 tin2-tang7 , thai2-tho2 thang liah8 pe7- bu2 khah iau3-kin2 Siong7-te3 ? 
  4 . Li2 kong2 Ia5-sou e5 kong-lo5 si7 chhin- chhiuN7 Lu2-o kap Chiok-liong5 , bong5-biau2 bo5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 . Hai3 ah ! Sian-siN chin7 chhin3-chhai2 kong2 . Lun7 Lu2-o Chiok- liong5 long2 si7 hong-tong5 boe7 sin3--tit ; Ia5- sou e5 tai7-chi3 , chiau5-pi7 ki3 ti7 seng3-chheh , beng5-beng5 thang chha5-kho2 , si7 sian-siN be7 bat thak8--tioh8 , thai2-tho2 bo5 thang chha5-kho2 ? Na7 kong2 gun2 e5 seng3-keng boe7 sin3--tit , chiu7 thiN-e7 long2 bo5 thang sin3 e5 chheh . 
