  II . Lun7 bok8-chu2 e5 lai5-lek8
  Bok8-chu2 tui3 sim2-mih8 si5 sim2-mih8 lang5 siat-khi2 , si7 oh-tit chai ; u7 lang5 kong2 si7 tui3 hou7-Han3 Teng-lan5 siat-khi2 . Teng- lan5 khi2-thau5 chin7 put-hau3, i teh choh- chhan5 , in lau7-bu2 tak8-jit8 koaN7-png7 khi3 hou7 i chiah8 , tak8-pai2 to hou7 Teng-lan5 phah , cha2 hiam5 cha2, oaN3 hiam5 oaN3; u7 chit8-jit8 Teng-lan5 ti7 chhan5--nih8 khoaN3-kiN3 iuN5-a2- kiaN2 chiah8 lin, cheng5 kha kui7-teh , Teng- lan5 ka-ki7 siuN7 kong2 , Cheng-siN siong7- chhiaN2 oe7 hiau2-tit heng5-hau3 , ho5-hong3 goa2 si7 lang5, kiam2 thang an2-ni phah lau7- bu2 mah ? Tui3 an2-ni tiaN7-tioh8 beh choe3 iu2- hau3 e5 kiaN2 . Hit jit8-tau3 i-e5 lau7-bu2 koh koaN7- png7 lai5 , Teng-lan5 kin2-kin2 chau2 beh khi3 chih ; in lau7-bu2 liah8 choe3 iu7 beh koh lai5 phah , chiu7 kin2-kin2 thiau3-loh8 chui2 . Teng-lan5 koaN2-kin2 thiau3-loh8 khi3 kiu3 , chhe7 long2 bo5, tok8-tok8 chhe7-tioh8 chit8-phiN3 pang, chiu7 chiong hit-phiN3 pang theh8- to3-khi3 khek choe3 siong7 , au7-lai5 lang5 chiah u7 chhong3 chit-e5 bok8-chu2 . U7 lang5 kong2 m7-si7 tui3 Teng-lan5, si7 khah-cha2 chiu7 u7; chiu7-si7 tui3 Bu2-ong5 , in-ui7 su2-ki3 kong2, “ Bu2-ong5 kau2--ni5 khi3 tang--si3 koan-peng ti7 Beng7-tin , choe3 Bun5-ong5 e5 bok8-chu2 , chai3 ti7 chhia-lai7 , chheng ka-ki7 choe3 Thai3-chu2 Hoat ; i3-su3 si7 kong2 , hong7 Bun5- ong5 lai5 hoat8 Tiu7 , hian2-beng5 ka-ki7 m7-kaN2 chu2-choan5 . ” Chong2-si7 su2-ki3 sui-bong2 an2-ni kong2, goa2 iah8 m7-kaN2 toan3 si7 tui3 Bu2-ong5 siat-khi2 ; kiam2-chhai2 Bu2-ong5 e5 tai7-seng i2-keng u7 , chiu7 Bun5-ong5 bio7-lai7 iah8 i2-keng u7 Bun5-ong5 e5 bok8-chu2, put-ko3 si7 kau3 Bu2-ong5 beh khi3 hoat8 Tiu7 hit-si5 chiah koh leng7-goa7 chhong3 chit8-sin ; m7-si7 kau3 beh hoat8 Tiu7 hit-si5 chiah chhong3 . Chhin-chhiuN7 Chhun-chhiu e5 si5 Hoan5- kong tauh8-tauh8 ai3 khi2-peng , iah8 chhong3 nng7 sin bok8-chu2 , na7 beh chhut-tin7 chiu7 chah chit8-sin khi3 , na7 to3-lai5 chiu7 iu5-goan5 chhai7 ti7 chou2-bio7--nih8 ; kiam2-chhai2 Bu2- ong5 iah8 si7 hit-ho7 khoan2 . Chiau3 goa2 phah-sng3 chng7 Giau5 Sun3 hit-si5 i2-keng u7 , in-ui7 Su-keng kong2 , Giau5 u7 Bun5-chou2- bio7 , Ge7-chou2 bio7 , iah8 Sun3 u7 khi3 che3 ; taN u7 bio7 tek-khak u7 bok8-chu2 , na7 bo5 , siu7-che3 e5 mih8 chiu7 beh che3 si7-chui7 ? Kiam2- chhai2 u7 lang5 kong2 bo5 tek-khak , in-ui7 cha2 e5 lang5 teh che3 u7 eng7 gin2-a2 chheng7 sian-jin5 e5 i-hok8 choe3 chu2-che3 e5 lang5 ,lang5 che3 i , i3-su3 si7 che3 chou2-kong ; kau3 au7- lai5 e5 lang5 hiam5 chit-ho7 hoat-tou7 m7-ho2 , in-ui7 chiau3 chit-ho7 hoat-tou7 chiu7 pe7 tioh8 pai3 kiaN2 , an2-ni ai3 beh iu2-hau3 tai7-seng biat8 jin5-lun5 , sou2-i2 u7 oaN7 bok8-chu2 ,hoe3 hit- e5 si e5 tai7-chi3 , an2-ni bok8-chu2 si7 khah au7- tai7 e5 lang5 chiah siat ; goa2 kong2 m7-si7 an2- ni , Tiong-kok chheh beng5-beng5 kong2 “ Chu2 sou2-i2 i sin5 , si sou2-i2 siong7-sin5 . ” ( I3-su3 si7 kong2 , bok8-chu2 si7 beh hou7 sin5 thang i- oa2 , si si7 beh hian2-beng5 sin5 e5 khoan2 . ) An2-ni si kap bok8-chu2 si7 tang5-si5 u7--e5 , chong2-si7 tu2-tu2 tui3 ti7-si5 u7 , goa2 m7-kaN2 toan3 , iau2-ku2 kaN2 kong2 chng7 Giau5-Sun3 e5 si5 i2- keng u7 .
  III . Gi7-lun7 chhai7 bok8-chu2 e5 m7-tioh8 
  Lun7 hit-e5 m7-tioh8 u7 kui2-na7 hang7. 1 . Peh-siN3 lang5 boe7 chhai7--tit . Beh chhai7 sin5-chu2 tek-khak tioh8 u7 thou2-toe7 e5 jin5-kun chiah oe7 choe3-tit, chhin-chhiuN7 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , kap u7 chhai2-te7 e5 kheng, chi2 kui2 teng2-ho7 e5 lang5 chiah oe7 chhai7--tit . Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 mng7 kong2 . An2-ni chiu7 Tai7-hu , Su7 , i2-kip8 peh-siN3 lang5 beh che3 beh chaiN2-iuN7 ? In3 kong2 , Put-ko3 si7 phou ki2-toh , chhioh8 , lai5 hou7 sin5 oa2 na7- tiaN7 . Sian-jin5 Khong2--si7 , TiN7--si7 , Chhui- si7 , chu3 Le2-ki3 che3-hoat hit-phiN long2-si7 an2-ni kong2; chong2-si7 u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 saN-pok, in-ui7 Le2-ki3 lai7 bo5 beng5-beng5 an2-ni kong2; sui-jian5 an2-ni iau2-ku2 Kong2-iong5 beng5-beng5 kong2 , “ Kheng, Tai7-hu, m7-si7 hit-ho7 u7 thou2-toe7 e5 Jin5-kun boe7 tit- thang khap-hiong2 chiau-bok8 . ” ( I3-su3 si7 hap8 che3 chou2-kong ) . An2-ni chiu7 beng5-beng5 si7 bo5 sin5-chu2 , in-ui7 na7-bo5 , chiu7 bo5 hun-piat8 chun-kui3 pi-chian7 e5 teng2-te7 . An2-ni chiu7 kin-a2-jit8 lang5-lang5 chhai7 sin5- chu2 , si7 peh-siN3 lang5 chhiam3 eng7 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 e5 le2-sou3 ; che si7 toa7 m7-tioh8 . Siat-su2 lang5 ai3 iu2-hau3 pe7-bu2 , hou7 i chheng7 ng5 leng5-pou5 chheng i choe3 hong5- te3 , an2-ni kiam2-oe7 thang kong2 , Goa2 si7 iu2- hau3 mah ? Cha2 Khong2-chu2 bo5 choe3-koaN bo5 ka-sin5 , tu2-tioh8 piN7 e5 si5 Chu2-Lou7 eng7 lang5 khi2 choe3 i-e5 ka-sin5 , Khong2-chu2 siong7-chhiaN2 tang7-tang7 chek-pi7 i, ho5-hong3 peh-siN3 chhiam3 Thian-chu2 e5 le2 , hit e5 m7-tioh8 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7 ah ? Kiam2- chhai2 u7 lang5 pok kong2, Le2-ki3 sou2-kong2 che3 e5 hoat-tou7 i2-kip8 sin5-chu2 chiah e5 tai7- chi3 , to bo5 kong2 si7 choan chi2 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , thai2-tho2 oe7 chai m7-si7 chi2 peh- siN3 lang5 ah ? In3 kong2, Le2-ki3 kong2 kau3 che3 , chiu7 soa3 kong2 bio7 , an2-ni thang chai m7- si7 chi2 peh-siN3 lang5 , in-ui7 peh-siN3 lang5 bo5 bio7 , put-ko3 che3 ti7 chhim2-sek na7-tiaN7 . 
  2 . Chiau3 le2-hoat , Thian-chu2 chhit-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 chhit-tai7 ; Chu-hou5 gou7-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 gou7-tai7 ; Tai7-hu saN-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 saN-tai7 ; Tek-su7 nng7-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 nng7-tai7 ; Koan-su chit8-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 chit8-tai7, iah8 soa3-chun2 peh-siN3 lang5 che3 chit8-tai7, chong2-si7 boe7 tit thang u7 bio7 . Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , Tai7-hu , in e5 chou2-kong na7 ke3 chhit-tai7 , gou7-tai7 , saN-tai7 , chiu7 bo5 chhai7 ti7 bio7--nih8 , put-ko3 si7 chhai7 ------------------------------------ 
  *Chit-chan5 e5 lai7-bin7 sou2 in2-khi2 chheh-- nih8 kui2-na7 ku3-oe7 , kiaN-liau2 bo5 thak8- chheh e5 hiaN-ti7 khoaN3-liau2 , be7 beng5-pek8 , taN beh khui-thiah tai7-liok8 hou7 lin2 thiaN . In-ui7 hit-tiap8 Liat8-kok e5 si5-chun7 , hia3-e5 kok long2 kui it-thong2 : it-thong2 e5 kok- kun kio3-cho3 Thian-chu2 , ki5-u5 hia3-e5 lai5 kui e5 kok , in-e5 kok-kun ho7-cho3 Chu-hou5 . Kok-lai7 e5 koaN-hu2 ho7-cho3 Tai7-hu . Boe7- soan2-chhut--khi3 cho3 koaN , siong7-teng2 e5 Thak8-chheh-lang5 ho7-cho3 Tek-su7 , tai7- khai3 chhin-chhiuN7 hian7-kim e5 Han7-lim5-iN7 . Su3-bin5-ka khi3 pan7 ge5-mng5 su7 ho7- cho3 Koan-su , tai7-khai3 chhin-chhiuN7 hian7- si5 e5 pang5-kho . 
  ------------------------------------------------------------------------ ti7 toaN5--nih8 , sian7--nih8 ; iah8 bo5 chhin- chhiuN7 ti7 bio7-lai7 e5 si5 , u7 su3-si5 long2 che3 ; kau3 koh-khah ku2 chiu7 tai5 , long2 bo5 koh- chai3 che3 . Koh chit8-keng bio7 chi2 u7 chit8 sian sin5-chu2 ; cha2 Cheng-chu2 mng7 Khong2-chu2 kong2 , “ Bio7--nih8 u7 nng7-sian bok8-chu2 , che si7 tioh8 mah ? ” Khong2-chu2 kong2 , “ ThiN bo5 nng7 e5 jit8 , kok bo5 nng7 e5 ong5 , bio7 u7 nng7 e5 chu2 , chaiN2-iuN7 si7 le2 goa2 to boe7 hiau2--tit . ” TaN kin-a2-jit8 peh-siN3 lang5 chhai7 sin5-chu2 m7-na7 si7 che3 chit8-tai7 , saN-tai7 , gou7-tai7 , chhit-tai7 na7-tiaN7 , si7 u7-e5 chhai7 kau3 gou7-lak8 chap8 tai7 e5 sin5-chu2 , iah8 soa3 che3--i ; an2-ni si7 peh-siN3 chhiam3 Thian- chu2 Chu-hou5 e5 le2 , iah8 si7 beh pi2 i koh- khah toa7 ; m7 na7 an2-ni , iah8 si7 chiong kui2-chap8 sin e5 sin5-chu2 chai7 choe3 chit8-keng chit8-te3-toh , che kiam2 m7-si7 ui5-keh8 Khong2- chu2 e5 oe7 , poe7 kou2-cha2 e5 le2-sou3 mah ? 
  3 . Lun7 che3 e5 sou2-chai7 bo5 chiau3 kou2-cha2 e5 hoat-tou7. In-ui7 cha2 e5 hoat-tou7 , peh-siN3 lang5 boe7 tit-thang u7 chou2-bio7 , put-ko3 si7 che3 ti7 chhim2-sek; kin-a2-jit8 e5 lang5 long2 bo5 chiau3 chit-e5 hoat , sou2-u7 e5 sin5-chu2- pang , long2 si7 he7 ti7 thiaN toh teng2 liau2- liau2 ; che kiam2 m7-si7 m7-tioh8 ? U7 lang5 koh-khah toa7 m7-tioh8, chiu7-si7 khi2 su5-tng5 , mng5-bai5-teng2 sia2 “ Bou2-siN3 ka-biau7 ” . TaN peh-siN3-lang5 to m7-thang u7 bio7 , chaiN2-iuN7 sia2 bio7 ? Siat-su2 sia2 su5-tng5 iah8 si7 m7-tioh8 , in-ui7 peh-siN3 lang5 put-ko3 si7 che3 ti7 chhim2- sek na7-tiaN7 . U7 lang5 koh-khah toa7 m7- tioh8 , chiu7-si7 soa3 che3 ti7 bong7--nih8 ; kiam2- chhai2 u7 lang5 pok-kong2 , Che3-bong7 si7 tui3 cha2 chiu7 u7, thai2-tho2 m7-tioh8 ? Cheng- chu2 kong2 , “ Thai5 gu5 lai5 che3-bong7 m7-tah8- tioh8 than3 pe7-bu2 ti7--teh , eng7 ti , koe , lai5 hok8-sai7 i . ” Beng7-chu2 kong2 , “ Hit e5 Che5- jin5 khi3 tang-mng5 goa7 chhe7 thiong2-bong7-- nih8 teh che3 e5 lang5. ” An2-ni che3-bong7 chu7-cha2 chiu7 u7, thai2-tho2 m7-tioh8 ? Goa2 kong2 , M7-si7 an2-ni ; Cheng-chu2 sou2-kong2 e5 che3-bong7 , si7 tu2-a2 khi3 tai5 hit-si5 lai5 che3 , m7-si7 tai5 liau2-au7 siong5-siong5 khi3 che3 ; koh Cheng-chu2 kong2 chit-ku3 si7 in-ui7 khoaN3 lang5 tui3-tiong7 si2-au7 e5 che3 , khah iau3-kin2 siN-cheng5 e5 hok8-sai7 , sou2-i2 kong2 chit-ku3 ; an2-ni Cheng-chu2 sui-bong2 bo5 ka3-lang5 m7-sai2 che3-bong7 , iau2-ku2 beng5- beng5 si7 kong2 che3 bong7 si7 bo5 lou7-eng7 . Lun7-kau3 Beng7-chu2 sou2 kong2--e5 , tioh8 chai he m7-si7 ke2-siat u7 hit-e5 lang5 hit-e5 su7, put-ko3 si7 sit8-sit8 hit-e5 tai7-chi3 lai5 pi2-pok kiu5 hu3-kui3 li7-tat8 e5 lang5 na7-tiaN7; chhin-chhiuN7 i bat chit8-pai2 ka2-siat chit8-e5 Song3- kok e5 lang5 puih8 tiu7-a2 e5 tai7-chi3 lai5 gi7-lun7 khi3 e5 to7-li2 ; sou2-i2 m7-thang phah-sng3 cha2 e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 u7 che3-bong7 . Han3-tiau5 Chhoa3 Iong u7 kong2 , “ Goa2 thiaN-kiN3 cha2 bo5 che3-bong7 e5 tai7-chi3 . ” Gui7 Bun5-te3 kong2 , “ Kut-thau5 m7-chai thiaN3 , m7-chai chiuN7 , thiong2-bong7 m7-si7 sin5 tiam3 e5 ui7 , chiau3-le2 bo5 che3-bong7 . ” ThiaN-hu-chu2 kong2 , “ Ho2 e5 le2 bo5 tiam3 khong3-ia2 lai5 kiaN5 , sou2-i2 siN bo5 tiam3 khong3-ia2 hap8 , si2 bo5 tiam3 khong3-ia2 che3 . ” Han3-tiau5 TiN7 Hian5 chu3 le2-ki3 iah8 kong2 , cha2 bo5 che3 bong7 ; siat-su2 i kong2 m7-tioh8 , chaiN2-iuN7 tng-si5 long2 bo5 lang5 pok i ah ? Cha2 bo5 che3- bong7 te7 it beng5 e5 pin5-ku3 chiu7-si7 khoaN3 Khong2-chu2, le2-ki3 tan5-kiong hit-phiN u7 kong2 , Khong2-chu2 soe3-han3 pe7 si2 , kau3 au7- lai5 in lau7-bu2 iah8 si2 , Khong2-chu2 i3-su3 beh ka7 in hap8-chong3 , m7 chai in lau7-pe7 e5 bong7 ti7 tah-loh8 , chiu7 mng7 Liau5-ban7-hu2 e5 lau7-bu2 chiah chai-ui7 , jian5-au7 hap8- chong3 ti7 Hong5. Siat-su2 Khong2-chu2 u7 chiuN7-soaN che3-bong7 , thai2-tho2 oe7 m7-chai- ui7 in lau7-pe7 e5 bong7 ? 
  4 .Goa2 thak8 le2-ki3 che3-gi7 , che3-hoat , che3- thong2 chiah e5 phiN , u7 kong2 ka7 ta-pou- lang5 lip8 sin5-chu2 lai5 che3 , be7-bat thiaN-kiN3 kong2 u7 ka7 hu7-jin5-lang5 lip8 sin5-chu2 lai5 che3 ; sou2-i2 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , Tai7-hu teng2 , sou2 che3--e5 long2 si7 sian-kun , sian- ong5 , sian-kong , sian-chou2 ; be7-bat thiaN-kiN3 u7 sian thai3-hou7 , sian hu-jin5 , sian chou2- ma2 , sian bu2-chhin . Au7-tai7 e5 lang5 chu7-chok chhong-beng5 , phah-sng3 kong2 cha2 seng3-ong5 seng3-jin5 iau2 bo5 chim-chiok , che3 lam5 bo5 che3 lu2 , sim beh thai2-tho2 oe7 peng5-an ? Tui3 an2-ni lip8 sian-kong e5 bok8- chu2 , iah8 lip8 sian-ma2 e5 bok8-chu2 , phah- sng3 ti3-sek beh ke3-thau5 seng3-jin5 , iu2-hau3 beh ke3-thau5 seng3-jin5 , kong-lo5 beh ke3- thau5 seng3-jin5 . Sit8-chai7 si7 toa7-toa7 put-kham ; siat-su2 si7 chu7-cha2 sou2 siat iah8-si7 u7 chho3 , lan2 Tiong-kok lam5-lu2 hun-piat8 chin-giam5 . Chiau3 le2-ki3 kong2 , Lam5-lu2 m7- thang chham-chham teh-che7, m7-thang tang5 chit8-e5 saN-a2-ke3 , m7-thang tang5 chit8 tiau5 soe2 sin-khu e5 kun, m7-thang saN oa2, m7-thang saN-chioh-mng7; kou chi2-be7 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 i2-keng ke3 , to3-lai5 choe3-kheh, hiaN- ti7 m7-thang kap i tang5 toh chiah8 . Sou2 kim3 u7 e5 sui-bong2 si7 siuN-giam5, chong2-si7 u7-e5 tek-khak si7 tioh8 than3, tang5-toh chiah8 na7 thang , tang5-chhng5 khun3 tek-khak si7 boe7 choe3 tit . TaN e5 lang5 lip8 bok8-chu2 , u7-e5 si7 lam5-chu2 , u7 e5 si7 lu2-chu2, chhai7-lai7 choe3 chit8-tui ; phi3-ju7 ta-koaN si2 , chiu7 chhai7 chit8-sin ta-koaN e5 sin5-chu2 ti7 toh-teng2 ; au7- lai5 sim-pu7 si2 , iah8 chhai7 chit8-sin sim-pu7 e5 bok8-chu2 ti7 toh-teng2 ; chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni hap8-le2 mah ? Na7 kong2 bok8-chu2 si7 si2-si2 e5 mih8 boe7 chai , chiu7 mih-sai2 chhai7 , mih- sai2 che3 ? Na7 kong2 si7 u7 chai, chiu7 lam5-lu2 hun7-chhng5, me5-jit8 choe3-tui, hit te3 toh na2 bin5-chhng5, chiu7 lam5-lu2 tang5-chhng5; chin7-chai7 kho2-ouN3, chin7-chai7 kian3-siau3. Choe3 kiaN2-sun e5 lang5 khoan2-thai7 chou2-kong an2-ni, si7 leng5-jiok8 chou2-kong, soa3 leng5-jiok8 pun2-sin, thai2-tho2 si7 iu2-hau3 ?
  5 . Chiau3 le2-ki3 che3-hoat hit phiN u7 kong2- khi2 sim2-mih8 ho7 lang5 chiah e7 kham-tit siu7 che3 ; i kong2 , “ U7 ho2 hoat-tou7 si kau3 peh-siN3 , chiah che3--i ; ui7 kok chhut-lat8 kau3 si2 chiah che3--i ; eng7 tioh8-boa5 hou7 kok an-tiaN7 , chiah che3--i ; oe7 tu5 toa7 chai- e7 , chiah che3--i ; oe7 ti2-tng toa7 hoan7-lan7 , chiah che3--i . ” Beh siu7 che3 tek-khak tioh8 u7 chi2 gou7-hang7 e5 chit8-hang7 , na7 bo5 , chiu7 long2 boe7-tit-thang siu7 che3 , Sou2-i2 Sun3 bo5 chou2 Kou-bong5 , bo5 chong Kou2-sou2, hoan2-tng2 chou2 Chhoan-hiok lai5 chong Giau5 ; an2-ni si7 bo5 chong sou2 chhin , si7 chong u7 tek-heng7--e5 ; keng-chheh long2 chiau5-pi7 , chha5-kho2 oe7 chai . TaN e5 lang5 m7-bat hoat-tou7 , put-lun7 pe7-bu2 si7 ho2-lang5 a2-si7 phaiN2-lang5 , si7 kun-chu2 a2-si7 siau2-jin5 , long2 bo5 iau3-kin2 ; put-ko3 pe7-bu2 na7 chit8- e7 si2 chiu7 lip8 sin5-chu2 lai5 che3--i ; siat-su2 pe7-bu2 oe7 kham-tit siu7 , to bo5 kong2 , siat- su2 boe7 kham-tit siu7 , iah8 lip8 sin5-chu2 lai5 che3 ; an2-ni si7 phian3-lang5 phian3-thiN , hai7 pe7-bu2 hoan7-tioh8 chhiam3-koan5 put-gi7 e5 choe7, choe3 sian-ong5 e5 choe7-jin5 , chhim- chhim thang thou2-khui3 . 
  6 . Chiau3 cha2 e5 hoat-tou7 lang5 teh-beh che3 e5 tai7-seng tioh8 chhit-jit8 kai3 saN-jit8 chai ; be7 che3 e5 si5-chun7 , chiu7 i2-keng u7 chit8- tiam2 iu-bun7 , siau3-liam7, it-tioh8 e5 sim ; ti3- kau3 teh che3 e5 si5 , giam2-jian5 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 pe7-bu2 . TaN e5 lang5 long2 bo5 an2-ni ; beh- che3 e5 si5 , iah8 bo5 pi7-pan7 , teh-che3 iah8 bo5 keng3-sim, che3-liau2 chiu7 pun mih8 to3--khi3 in-tau ; u7-si5 khah u7 mih8, chiu7 soa3 chhiaN2 peng5-iu2 lai5 chiah8 chiu2, u7-si5 soa3 hoah-kun5 , kong3 iang5-khim5, kio3 ge7-toaN3 , chiong chou2-kong e5 chiN5 ka-ki7 khai , khai hou7 chou2-kong pe7-bu2 che7-siau3. U7-si5 pe7-bu2 oah8-teh e5 si5-chun7 khun5-khou2 liap8-chek, kau3 si2-au7 kiaN2-sun an2-ni-siN khai, mia5 si7 hau3 chou2-kong , sit8 si7 hau3 ka-ki7 ; chou2-kong na7 ti7 im-kan oe7 chai, tek-khak tng3-kha tio5-toe7 , ka7-ge5 chhiat-chhi2 , kong2 , Goa2 hiah e5 chiN5 si7 khun5-khiam7 liap8-chek kui2-chap8 ni5 , lin2 bo5 po2-sioh hong3-sim khai , chin-si7 put-hau3 kiaN2 . U7-e5 ka-ki7 bo5 chiN5 chiu7 si3-koe3 oaiN-chioh, kau3 au7-lai5 lang5 beh tho2 , bo5 thang heng5--lang5, tui3 an2-ni hou7 lang5 chhoh-me7 , leng5-jiok8 pe7- bu2 ; an2-ni in-ui7 ka-ki7 e5 chiah8 hai7 pe7-bu2 kian3-siau3 , kiam2 si7 iu2-hau3 mah ? 
